  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `1.7.2`\r\nOS & Version: Linux (Gentoo AMD64)\r\nCommit hash : 1db4ecdc\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nGeth updates the blockchain on first start.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nGeth crashes with a stacktrace during update\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nRan the following command: `./geth --fast --cache=2048`\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\nINFO [11-12|12:53:21] Imported new block headers               count=0    elapsed=12.895ms  number=1596 hash=f3a659…138925 ignored=384\r\nINFO [11-12|12:53:21] Imported new block receipts              count=35   elapsed=811.568µs bytes=7161   number=1247 hash=63d553…7d080f ignored=0\r\nINFO [11-12|12:53:22] Imported new block receipts              count=349  elapsed=5.491ms   bytes=50649  number=1596 hash=f3a659…138925 ignored=0\r\nINFO [11-12|12:53:22] Imported new block headers               count=0    elapsed=54.263ms  number=3644 hash=50cb51…fd74f2 ignored=2048\r\npanic: runtime error: growslice: cap out of range\r\n\r\ngoroutine 9272 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp.(*encbuf).encodeString(0xc42029e3c0, 0xc45370efc0, 0xffffff3bb85b73f8, 0xffffff3bb85b73f8)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp/encode.go:208 +0x1d5\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp.writeByteArray(0xea4da0, 0xc45370efc0, 0x191, 0xc42029e3c0, 0xea4da0, 0xc45370efc0)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp/encode.go:457 +0xe2\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp.makeStructWriter.func1(0xf03ea0, 0xc45370efc0, 0x199, 0xc42029e3c0, 0xc45370efc0, 0x199)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp/encode.go:537 +0x173\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp.makePtrWriter.func4(0xe46a60, 0xc45370efc0, 0x16, 0xc42029e3c0, 0x0, 0x0)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp/encode.go:580 +0xe6\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp.(*encbuf).encode(0xc42029e3c0, 0xe46a60, 0xc45370efc0, 0xea38a0, 0xc42029e3c0)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp/encode.go:188 +0xe6\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp.Encode(0x7f996c279030, 0xc457528540, 0xe46a60, 0xc45370efc0, 0x0, 0x0)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rlp/encode.go:89 +0x103\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/types.rlpHash(0xe46a60, 0xc45370efc0, 0xc447a48ea8, 0x40ade6, 0xc4478c2ea0, 0xf310ae)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/types/block.go:126 +0xbf\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/types.(*Header).Hash(0xc45370efc0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/types/block.go:102 +0x62\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/consensus/ethash.(*Ethash).verifyHeaderWorker(0xc4200a4300, 0x182ce60, 0xc4204ee780, 0xc4449f0000, 0x800, 0x2980, 0xc455bd8800, 0x800, 0x800, 0x696, ...)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/consensus/ethash/consensus.go:156 +0x2ca\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/consensus/ethash.(*Ethash).VerifyHeaders.func1(0xc45022d6e0, 0xc444fd0000, 0x800, 0x800, 0xc4200a4300, 0x182ce60, 0xc4204ee780, 0xc4449f0000, 0x800, 0x2980, ...)\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/consensus/ethash/consensus.go:116 +0xff\r\ncreated by github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/consensus/ethash.(*Ethash).VerifyHeaders\r\n        /home/travis/gopath/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/consensus/ethash/consensus.go:114 +0x2d8\r\n\r\n````\r\n",
